    },
    {
      "id": "d4-ann1-bg",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 320,
      "width": 280,
      "height": 175,
      "backgroundColor": "#fff3bf",
      "strokeColor": "#e8590c",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "roundness": {
        "type": 3
      },
      "createdAt": "2026-03-05T07:59:57.933Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-05T08:00:08.802Z",
      "version": 2,
      "groupIds": [
        "mmd6dx0alxdqfr8erf"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "d4-ann1-text",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 75,
      "y": 330,
      "width": 250,
      "strokeColor": "#495057",
      "roughness": 0,
      "text": "Why can't the webview fetch data?\n\nProblem: The webview runs in a locked-\ndown browser sandbox. Its security\npolicy blocks ALL network requests.\n\nSolution: The webview sends a message\nto the extension, the extension makes\nthe API call, and sends the data back.\nAll data is proxied through the host.",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "createdAt": "2026-03-05T07:59:57.933Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-05T08:00:08.800Z",
      "version": 2,
      "groupIds": [
        "mmd6dx0alxdqfr8erf"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "d4-ann2-bg",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 360,
      "y": 320,
      "width": 280,
      "height": 175,
      "backgroundColor": "#fff3bf",
      "strokeColor": "#e8590c",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "roundness": {
        "type": 3
      },
      "createdAt": "2026-03-05T07:59:57.933Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-05T08:00:09.247Z",
      "version": 2,
      "groupIds": [
        "mmd6dxcq7ae74zzwd58"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "d4-ann2-text",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 375,
      "y": 330,
      "width": 250,
      "strokeColor": "#495057",
      "roughness": 0,
      "text": "Stale response problem\n\nProblem: User clicks skill A, then\nquickly clicks skill B. If A's response\narrives after B's, it overwrites the page.\n\nSolution: A counter increments on each\nrequest. Before sending any response,\ncheck if this is still the latest request.\nOld responses are silently dropped.",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "createdAt": "2026-03-05T07:59:57.933Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-05T08:00:09.250Z",
      "version": 2,
      "groupIds": [
        "mmd6dxcq7ae74zzwd58"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "d4-ann3-bg",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 660,
      "y": 320,
      "width": 280,
      "height": 175,
      "backgroundColor": "#fff3bf",
      "strokeColor": "#e8590c",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "roundness": {
        "type": 3
      },
      "createdAt": "2026-03-05T07:59:57.933Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-05T08:00:09.689Z",
      "version": 2,
      "groupIds": [
        "mmd6dxp172x9jt7lh3e"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "d4-ann3-text",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 675,
      "y": 330,
      "width": 250,
      "strokeColor": "#495057",
      "roughness": 0,
      "text": "Preventing XSS from scraped HTML\n\nProblem: We inject HTML scraped from\nskills.sh into the webview. A malicious\nscript tag could execute.\n\nSolution: Every render generates a\nrandom 32-character token (nonce).\nOnly scripts with that exact token can\nrun. Injected scripts don't have it.",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "createdAt": "2026-03-05T07:59:57.933Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-05T08:00:09.691Z",
      "version": 2,
      "groupIds": [
        "mmd6dxp172x9jt7lh3e"
      ]
    },
